  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cardiovascular &amp; echocardiographic assessment in pregnant women with hypertension during
      their pregnancy in comparison to Pregnant normotensive women.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Cardiovascular &amp; echocardiographic assessment in pregnant women with hypertension during
      their pregnancy in comparison to Pregnant normotensive women. Also,comparing
      echocardiographic parameters in hypertensive pregnant women being treated with either alfa
      methyl dopa or labetolol.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
